cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY 

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on robot manipulation of deformable objects. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper involves visual state estimation of the deformable object. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper proposes a self-supervised learning objective for state estimation and uses a neural network dynamics model. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper involves planning manipulation actions and incorporating physics priors. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper involves model-based control of a physical system.
